Package: pixelruller
Version: @VERSION@
Section: graphics
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Theologos Kalotrapezis <kalotrapezis@users.noreply.github.com>
Depends: python3
Recommends: xdg-user-dirs
Suggests: spectacle, gnome-screenshot, mate-utils, xfce4-screenshooter, grim, flameshot, scrot, maim, shutter
Homepage: https://github.com/kalotrapezis/PixelRuller
Description: pixel-perfect screenshot measurement and AI UI design tool
 PixelRuller measures and annotates screenshots, designs responsive desktop
 interfaces with semantic widgets, and exports a shared canonical design that
 humans and AI collaborators can edit and implement together.
